{"tid":2365620,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內地新增124宗本地確診，河北有一宗死亡個案","createTime":"2021-01-14T01:51:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T05:34:35.000Z","uid":278587,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"383a2560668d6f9dd9564b31632ec897a82587be","tid":2365620,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T01:51:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=420223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D420223&d=9I4RHoMADcqvkoBT02AJuGqRhi9KU01BjP2Z1UqMPtI%3D&h=0fdcec5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D420223&h=f09eaab4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=420223</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】內地過去一日新增124宗新冠病毒本地確診，單日本地確診數字連續兩日破百，河北有一宗死亡個案。<br />\n<br />\n國家衞健委公布，過去一日共有138宗新冠病毒確診，其中124宗是本地個案，河北與黑龍江分別有81宗及43宗，另外新增一宗死亡病例，是河北的本土個案。"},{"pid":"85c9ef6b6c03e5048174cb55c51b006a0c2bce27","tid":2365620,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T01:53:37.000Z","msg":"說好的清零<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a236127016e7dbca25a9adcbb781c265298cdc8b","tid":2365620,"uid":123738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T01:54:34.000Z","msg":"唔係掛，死一隻支那狗都報？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣做壞規矩噃"},{"pid":"b7e0a7c744f1be5d89964e2c726c9be94d8592c7","tid":2365620,"uid":103050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T01:55:10.000Z","msg":"支共最愛既無症狀感染有幾多宗？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae1f18e61d91641e1d5e6d02d2af96d102238382","tid":2365620,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T01:56:23.000Z","msg":"支式抗疫<i